## 👨‍💻 About Me

I'm an **AI-native engineer** specializing in **Large Language Models** and **Computer Vision**, with a strong foundation in **Go**, **JavaScript**, and full-stack web technologies. I build intelligent systems that bridge cutting-edge AI research with production-ready applications.

```go
package main

type Engineer struct {
    Name        string
    Focus       []string
    WorkStyle   string
    CurrentGoal string
}

func main() {
    me := Engineer{
        Name:        "Timothy Yusuf",
        Focus:       []string{"LLMs", "Computer Vision", "AI Systems"},
        WorkStyle:   "Remote-First",
        CurrentGoal: "Build impactful AI solutions",
    }
}

